  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p>To provide general administrative duties, support the sales team and other ad hoc duties when required.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Handle frontline clerical duties:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attend to telephone calls and answering general enquiries</li>\n  <li>Receive walk-in visitors</li>\n  <li>Provide general administrative and project-based work support</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Support duties:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Key in invoices</li>\n  <li>Receiving stocks</li>\n  <li>Transferring stocks</li>\n  <li>Inventories control</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Working Hours:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Monday to Friday - 8.30am to 5.45pm</li>\n  <li>alternate Saturdays - 8.30am to 12.30pm</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>West area</li>\n  <li>Skill: Knowledge of Adobe Photoshop</li>\n  <li>Min. O’ Levels or equivalent with passes in English, Chinese and Mathematics</li>\n  <li>Bilingual in English and Chinese, both oral and written so as to communicate with Mandarin speaking customers / suppliers</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of similar working experience is a plus.</li>\n  <li>Team player and a fast learner, someone who is energetic with good people management skills and able to work independently in a fast paced environment.</li>\n  <li>Able to start immediately.</li>\n  <li>Singaporeans only.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
